source.name: Social Characteristic data, all planning districts: American Community Survey, 2005-2009
source.description: An excel spreadsheet containing social characteristic data for all Boston planning districts from the American Community Survey 2005-2009. The data in this spreadsheet were used to create the BRA's ACS planning district reports.
